<h2>Margarita</h2>
<img src="Margarita.jpg" height=400 width=100 align= "middle" class= "center">
<h3> A classic cocktail thats super easy to make and guaranteed to impress. </h3>
<h2> Ingredients</h2>
<h3> 50ml tequila</h3>
<h3> 1.5 tbsp of lime juice </h3>
<h3> 1.5 tbsp of triple sec </h3>
<h3> Salt and lime to garnish! </h3>
<h2> Instructions </h2>
<h3>Put salt on a saucer, wipe the rim of the glass with lime and dunk the rim of the glass in the salt.</h3>
<h3> Stir the ingredients together with ice. If you’re fancy use a cocktail shaker, but ultimately a spoon and jug will suffice. </h3>
<h3> Strain into a chilled martini glass. Serve with a slice of lime. </h3>
<h3> Enjoy! Try not to use a straw to save the turtles and other various marine life...</h3>
